Attacks
--------------------------------------
XSS
CSRF
FIXATION ATTACK
HQL Injection


Measures
-------------------------------------
Verifies Input in both Client side and Server Side for Type, Length, Format and Range
Password Encryption using Salt
Platform does not accept file paths from the user to avoid canonicalization issues


